    • \(\begin{aligned} S(X,Y)=\frac{\sum_{i=1}^p X_i Y_i}{\sqrt{ \sum_{i=1}^p X_i^2 \cdot \sum_{i=1}^p Y_i^2}}\end{aligned}\)

  • ( ): X Y
